title: Trade, Mueller & Trump Tax Returns

description:
Guests include Jake Sherman and Anna Palmer, senior writers for Politico, coauthors of Politico Playbook, authors of the new book, "THE HILL TO DIE ON." Also, Kim Wallace, former assistant secretary for legislative affairs at the Treasury Department under President Obama's administration.
